originalText.text: DO NOT USE THIS CAR SERVICE. I received the WORST disrespectful, appalling, unacceptable customer service from a man who gave me his name as "Jose" last name "Bete para el carajo" which is a curse phrase in spanish meaning go to hell. He yelled at me and hung up the phone. I am a disabled person walking down 4 flights of steps. NO ELEVATOR.  I deserved a bit of grace and consideration.  Not verbal abuse. I will NEVER use this service again and will tell my friends and family to avoid them as well. Worth noting I was on time! I shudder to Imagine how they treat someone who is late.

Professional Car service needs to be shut down immediately.
